data.description: The home is being sold 'AS Is' Seller to do no repairs, and no inspections.  Beautiful spacious ranch home, Great floor plan entry foyer, large family room, dining room, kitchen, and great living room.  This home has 4 Bedroom, 2 Baths looking for a new owner.  Property needs some TLC, but this all brick ranch home is in a great location.  Motivated Seller please submit all reasonable offers.
